songs.title: Female Moving
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
Know she wanna ride wit' a real nigga
Smokin', drinkin', lean poppin' pills
Aye, since a youngin' been a real nig'
Totin' straps, movin' shit, makin' deals nig'
Aye, for a real one she move yeah, for a real one yeah she move yeah
For a real one yeah she movin', aye, for a real one yeah she movin'

[Verse 1]
I just moved out to the coast, man I leave her alone aye
I put her in VLONE, [?]
Poppin' tags throughout the season
Makin' bread, hittin' stains, I had a reason
Bad lil' thing, put her in a new Range
She wanna play wit' me, said "fuckin' do yo' thang"

[Chorus]
Know she wanna ride wit' a real nigga
Smokin', drinkin', lean poppin' pills
Aye, since a youngin' been a real nig'
Totin' straps, movin' shit, makin' deals nig'
Aye, for a real one she move yeah, for a real one yeah she move yeah
For a real one yeah she movin', aye, for a real one yeah she movin'
